        <h3>Advanced Networking II Case Study</h3>
        <p class="project-date"><i class="far fa-calendar"></i> April 2026</p>
        <p>Designed and deployed a multi-site LAN/WAN infrastructure across Toronto, Ottawa, and Oshawa. Configured MPLS WAN, DMVPN Phase 3 with IPSec (AES-256, SHA-512), VTPv3, PAgP/LACP EtherChannels, Spanning Tree, and HSRPv2. Verified connectivity via TCL scripting and NHRP/IPSec SA validation.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span>Cisco Packet Tracer</span><span>MPLS</span><span>DMVPN</span>
          <span>EIGRP</span><span>IPSec</span><span>SecureCRT</span>
